Selection

select * from customer;

select * from customer where customer_id='Cust_01';

select * from customer where customer_street='Main';



Output:

+-------------+-----------------------+-----------------+---------------+
| customer_id | customer_name         | customer_street | customer_city |
+-------------+-----------------------+-----------------+---------------+
