Combination of Projection and Selection

select customer_id from customer where customer_city='Palayamkottai';


select customer_id,customer_name from customer where customer_street='south';


Output:

+-------------+
| customer_id |
+-------------+
| Cust_09     |
+-------------+
+-------------+------------------+
| customer_id | customer_name    |
+-------------+------------------+
| Cust_02     | Bharkavi D E     |
| Cust_07     | Javid Ali L      |
| Cust_12     | Sakunthaladevi S |
+-------------+------------------+

